name: Cut Panel to suit and primer the cutting edge
Nails flush with the panel surface
Use C-25 straight ‘T’ - Head stainless steel brad nail
Nail fix to Panel @ 600mm spacing maximal
Fixing needs to be 75mm away from top and bottom edge
Apply Bostik® Seal N Flex™ - 1 for Panel joint
Fixing T nails is 18mm from the underlap edge and 16mm from the overlap edge
